column2: SELECT A.ra, A.dec, A.objID, A.z, A.zerr, A.class, A.subClass, A.specobjID, A.specobjIDClean, D.oiii_#_flux, D.oiii_#_flux_err, E.logMass as logMassFGED, E.logMass_min as logMass_minFGED, E.logMass_max as logMass_maxFGED, E.ssfr as ssfrFGED, E.ssfr_min as ssfr_minFGED, E.ssfr_max as ssfr_maxFGED, F.logMass as logMassFGEND, F.logMass_min as logMass_minFGEND, F.logMass_max as logMass_maxFGEND, F.ssfr as ssfrFGEND, F.ssfr_min as ssfr_minFGEND, F.ssfr_max as ssfr_maxFGEND, G.logMass as logMassFGWD, G.logMass_min as logMass_minFGWD, G.logMass_max as logMass_maxFGWD, G.ssfr as ssfrFGWD, G.ssfr_min as ssfr_minFGWD, G.ssfr_max as ssfr_maxFGWD, H.logMass as logMassFGWND, H.logMass_min as logMass_minFGWND, H.logMass_max as logMass_maxFGWND, H.ssfr as ssfrFGWND, H.ssfr_min as ssfr_minFGWND, H.ssfr_max as ssfr_maxFGWND FROM MyDB.CasjobsCombinedOutputCtrl AS A OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (A.ra, A.dec, #/#.) AS B INNER JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS C ON B.objID = C.objID INNER JOIN galSpecLine as D ON C.specObjID = D.specObjID INNER JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranEarlyDust as E ON C.specObjID = E.specObjID INNER JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranEarlyNoDust as F ON C.specObjID = F.specObjID INNER JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranWideDust as G ON C.specObjID = G.specObjID INNER JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranWideNoDust as H ON C.specObjID = H.specObjID INTO MyDB.CTRLStellarMassGalSpecLine
